Birmingham is the rat capital of the UK and the London Borough of Southwark has the most mice , cockroaches and bed bugs .
The Midlands city topped the league table for the highest number of rat exterminations with almost 15,000 between 2013 and 2014 .
Newcastle is officially the most pest-infested place in the country with 5 per cent of people living on Tyneside residents the most likely to report a problem .